<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
# VersionTag: 2605.B5.V46.0
<!-- FileRole: XhtmlTool -->
<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN"
  "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en" lang="en">
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Changelog Viewer — PwShGUI Suite</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/pwshgui-base.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/pwshgui-responsive.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/accent-changelog.css" />
  <style type="text/css">
    body { font-family: Segoe UI, Tahoma, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #0d1117; color: #c9d1d9; display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-height: 100vh; }
    .app-bar { background: #161b22; border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d; padding: 10px 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
    .app-bar h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 18px; color: #2dd4bf; flex: 1; }
    .app-bar .version-tag { font-size: 11px; color: #484f58; }
    .tab-strip { display: flex; background: #161b22; border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d; overflow-x: auto; }
    .tab-strip button { font-family: Segoe UI, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background: transparent; color: #8b949e; border: none; padding: 8px 16px; cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s; white-space: nowrap; }
    .tab-strip button:hover { color: #c9d1d9; }
    .tab-strip button.active { color: #2dd4bf; border-bottom-color: #2dd4bf; }
    .main { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }
    .tab-panel { display: none; flex: 1; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }
    .tab-panel.active { display: flex; }
    .filter-bar { display: flex; gap: 8px; padding: 10px 16px; background: #161b22; border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; }
    .filter-bar label { font-size: 12px; color: #8b949e; font-weight: 600; }
    .filter-bar input, .filter-bar select { font-family: Segoe UI, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background: #0d1117; color: #c9d1d9; border: 1px solid #30363d; border-radius: 6px; padding: 5px 8px; }
    .filter-bar input[type="search"] { flex: 1; min-width: 180px; }
    .filter-bar input[type="date"] { width: 140px; }
    .filter-bar select { min-width: 120px; }
    .filter-bar button { font-family: Segoe UI, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; border: 0; border-radius: 6px; padding: 6px 12px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; }
    .btn-primary { background: #238636; color: #fff; }
    .btn-info { background: #1f6feb; color: #fff; }
    .btn-alt { background: #30363d; color: #c9d1d9; border: 1px solid #484f58; }
    .btn-warn { background: #d29922; color: #0d1117; }
    .btn-danger { background: #da3633; color: #fff; }
    .content-area { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 16px; }
    .version-block { background: #161b22; border: 1px solid #30363d; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .version-block h2 { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 16px; color: #2dd4bf; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
    .version-block h2 .date { font-size: 12px; color: #8b949e; font-weight: 400; }
    .version-block h3 { margin: 10px 0 4px; font-size: 13px; color: #58a6ff; }
    .version-block ul { margin: 0 0 6px 18px; padding: 0; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.7; }
    .version-block li { margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .version-block table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 6px; }
    .version-block table th { background: #21262d; color: #8b949e; padding: 5px 8px; text-align: left; font-weight: 600; }
    .version-block table td { padding: 5px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #21262d; }
    .tag { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; }
    .tag-added { background: #238636; color: #fff; }
    .tag-changed { background: #1f6feb; color: #fff; }
    .tag-fixed { background: #d29922; color: #0d1117; }
    .tag-removed { background: #da3633; color: #fff; }
    .tag-security { background: #7c3aed; color: #fff; }
    .tag-deprecated { background: #484f58; color: #c9d1d9; }
    .tag-pipeline { background: #2dd4bf; color: #0d1117; }
    .stats-strip { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(100px, 1fr)); gap: 8px; padding: 10px 16px; background: #161b22; border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d; }
    .stat-box { background: #21262d; border: 1px solid #30363d; border-radius: 6px; padding: 8px; text-align: center; }
    .stat-val { font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; color: #2dd4bf; }
    .stat-label { font-size: 10px; color: #8b949e; }
    .diff-panel { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex: 1; overflow: hidden; }
    .diff-side { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }
    .diff-side .diff-header { background: #21262d; padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 6px 6px 0 0; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #8b949e; }
    .diff-side .diff-body { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; background: #0d1117; border: 1px solid #30363d; border-radius: 0 0 6px 6px; padding: 10px; font-family: Consolas, monospace; font-size: 12px; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.6; }
    .diff-add { color: #7ee787; background: rgba(46,160,67,0.15); display: block; padding: 1px 4px; }
    .diff-del { color: #f85149; background: rgba(248,81,73,0.10); display: block; padding: 1px 4px; text-decoration: line-through; }
    .diff-ctx { color: #8b949e; display: block; padding: 1px 4px; }
    .combined-panel { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 16px; }
    .combined-panel .version-block { border-left: 3px solid #2dd4bf; }
    .mdv-banner { background: #21262d; border: 1px solid #30363d; border-radius: 6px; padding: 10px 14px; margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-size: 12px; color: #8b949e; }
    .mdv-banner code { background: #0d1117; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; color: #7ee787; font-family: Consolas, monospace; font-size: 11px; }
    .log-select { display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: center; }
    .empty-state { text-align: center; padding: 60px 20px; color: #484f58; font-size: 14px; }
    .empty-state .icon { font-size: 40px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .highlight { background: rgba(210,153,34,0.3); border-radius: 2px; padding: 0 2px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="app-bar">
    <h1>Changelog Viewer</h1>
    <span class="version-tag">PwShGUI Suite — 2604.B2.V33.3</span>
  </div>

  <div class="tab-strip" id="tabStrip">
    <button class="active" onclick="showTab('browse')">Browse</button>
    <button onclick="showTab('diff')">Differential</button>
    <button onclick="showTab('combined')">Combined View</button>
    <button onclick="showTab('mdv')">Virtual .mdv</button>
  </div>

  <div class="main">

    <!-- ═══════════ TAB 1: BROWSE ═══════════ -->
    <div class="tab-panel active" id="tabBrowse">
      <div class="filter-bar">
        <label>Log:</label>
        <select id="logSelect" onchange="loadChangelog()">
          <option value="CHANGELOG" selected="selected">CHANGELOG.md</option>
          <option value="ENHANCEMENTS-LOG">ENHANCEMENTS-LOG.md</option>
        </select>
        <label>Search:</label>
        <input type="search" id="searchInput" placeholder="Type to filter entries..." oninput="applyFilters()" />
        <label>From:</label>
        <input type="date" id="dateFrom" onchange="applyFilters()" />
        <label>To:</label>
        <input type="date" id="dateTo" onchange="applyFilters()" />
        <label>Category:</label>
        <select id="categoryFilter" onchange="applyFilters()">
          <option value="">All</option>
          <option value="Added">Added</option>
          <option value="Changed">Changed</option>
          <option value="Fixed">Fixed</option>
          <option value="Removed">Removed</option>
          <option value="Security">Security</option>
          <option value="Deprecated">Deprecated</option>
          <option value="Pipeline">Pipeline</option>
        </select>
        <label>Type:</label>
        <select id="typeFilter" onchange="applyFilters()">
          <option value="">All</option>
          <option value="sin">SIN Fix (⸸)</option>
          <option value="feature">Feature (⚙)</option>
          <option value="file">New File (📄)</option>
          <option value="manifest">Manifest (📋)</option>
          <option value="pipeline">Pipeline (🔁)</option>
          <option value="tracking">Tracking (📌)</option>
        </select>
        <button class="btn-alt" onclick="clearFilters()">Clear</button>
      </div>

      <div class="stats-strip" id="statsStrip">
        <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-val" id="statVersions">0</div><div class="stat-label">Versions</div></div>
        <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-val" id="statAdded">0</div><div class="stat-label">Added</div></div>
        <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-val" id="statChanged">0</div><div class="stat-label">Changed</div></div>
        <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-val" id="statFixed">0</div><div class="stat-label">Fixed</div></div>
        <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-val" id="statFiles">0</div><div class="stat-label">New Files</div></div>
        <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-val" id="statSins">0</div><div class="stat-label">SIN Fixes</div></div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-area" id="browseContent">
        <div class="empty-state"><div class="icon">📋</div>Loading changelog...</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════ TAB 2: DIFFERENTIAL ═══════════ -->
    <div class="tab-panel" id="tabDiff">
      <div class="filter-bar">
        <label>From Version:</label>
        <select id="diffFrom"></select>
        <label>To Version:</label>
        <select id="diffTo"></select>
        <button class="btn-info" onclick="computeDiff()">Compare</button>
        <button class="btn-primary" onclick="exportMdv()">Export .mdv</button>
      </div>
      <div class="diff-panel" id="diffContent">
        <div class="diff-side">
          <div class="diff-header" id="diffLeftHeader">Select versions to compare</div>
          <div class="diff-body" id="diffLeft"><div class="empty-state"><div class="icon">⇄</div>Pick two versions above</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="diff-side">
          <div class="diff-header" id="diffRightHeader">—</div>
          <div class="diff-body" id="diffRight"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════ TAB 3: COMBINED VIEW ═══════════ -->
    <div class="tab-panel" id="tabCombined">
      <div class="filter-bar">
        <label>From:</label>
        <select id="combFrom"></select>
        <label>To:</label>
        <select id="combTo"></select>
        <button class="btn-info" onclick="buildCombined()">Build Combined</button>
        <button class="btn-primary" onclick="exportCombinedMdv()">Export .mdv</button>
      </div>
      <div class="mdv-banner" id="combBanner" style="display:none;">
        Virtual combined changelog: <code id="combFilename">—</code>
        <span>All changes between selected versions merged into a single view</span>
      </div>
      <div class="combined-panel" id="combContent">
        <div class="empty-state"><div class="icon">📑</div>Select a range and click Build Combined</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════ TAB 4: VIRTUAL .mdv FILES ═══════════ -->
    <div class="tab-panel" id="tabMdv">
      <div class="filter-bar">
        <label>Generated .mdv files (temp/):</label>
        <select id="mdvSelect" onchange="loadMdv()">
          <option value="">— Select —</option>
        </select>
        <button class="btn-alt" onclick="refreshMdvList()">Refresh</button>
        <button class="btn-danger" onclick="clearMdvFiles()">Clear All</button>
      </div>
      <div class="content-area" id="mdvContent">
        <div class="empty-state"><div class="icon">📄</div>.mdv files are generated on-demand via Differential or Combined tabs.<br/>They are stored in <code>temp/changelog-mdv/</code></div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

<script type="text/javascript">
//<![CDATA[

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// STATE
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
var _versions = [];     // parsed version entries [{tag, date, sections:{Added:[],Changed:[],...}, raw:''}]
var _rawLines = [];     // raw markdown lines
var _mdvStore = [];     // [{filename, content, created}] in-memory .mdv store (persisted to localStorage)

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// TAB SWITCHING
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
function showTab(id) {
  var panels = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-panel');
  var btns   = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-strip button');
  for (var i = 0; i < panels.length; i++) { panels[i].className = 'tab-panel'; }
  for (var i = 0; i < btns.length; i++)   { btns[i].className = ''; }
  var map = { browse:'tabBrowse', diff:'tabDiff', combined:'tabCombined', mdv:'tabMdv' };
  document.getElementById(map[id]).className = 'tab-panel active';
  btns[['browse','diff','combined','mdv'].indexOf(id)].className = 'active';
  if (id === 'mdv') { refreshMdvList(); }
}

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// CHANGELOG PARSING
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
var CHANGELOG_CONTENT = [
'# VersionTag: 2605.B5.V46.0',
'<!-- VersionBuildHistory: 2604.B2.V33.4  2026-04-29  Restored, normalized, emoji-first formatting; 17 entries; gap-free contiguous timeline -->',
'<!-- FileRole: Changelog -->',
'',
'# 📚 PowerShellGUI — CHANGELOG',
'',
'> 📐 **Format:** [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/) adapted for PwShGUI',
'> 🏷 **Versioning:** `YYMM.B<build>.V<major>.<minor>` — see [DOC-ICON-STANDARD.md](DOC-ICON-STANDARD.md)',
'> 🔣 `⸸` SIN fix · `⚑` semi-SIN · `⚙` feature · `📋` manifest · `📄` new file · `🔁` pipeline · `📌` tracking · `💡` guidance · `🔒` security · `🐛` bug · `✅` verified',
'',
'---',
'',
'## [2604.B2.V33.4] — 2026-04-29',
'',
'### Added',
'- 📄 `scripts/Invoke-ObjectivePipelineCycle.ps1` — 11-iteration compounding pipeline runner with 5/4/3/2 recommendation cadence',
'- 📄 `~REPORTS/objective-pipeline-cycle-20260429-001704.json` — first cycle report evidence artifact',
'',
'### Changed',
'- ⚙ `tests/Invoke-GUISmokeTest.ps1` — repaired regex literal corruption (Export-ModuleMember pattern restored)',
'- ⚙ `scripts/Sync-ChangelogViewerData.ps1` — hardened Escape-JsLine (single-pass `\\` then `\'`); CDATA terminator escape; U+2028/U+2029 separators',
'- ⚙ `scripts/Sync-ChangelogViewerData.ps1` — Show-Objectives header added',
'- ⚙ `fix_update_version.ps1` — Outline footer added',
'- ⚙ `fix_check_version.ps1` — Outline footer added',
'- ⚙ `Launch-GUI-SmokeTest.bat` — objectives header added',
'',
'### Fixed',
'- ⸸ Resolved render regression — embedded JS string literal corruption (`\\\\\'` → SyntaxError) that blanked the changelog viewer',
'- ⸸ P004/P022 — strict-mode `$1` interpolation bug in Invoke-ObjectivePipelineCycle resolved',
'- 🐛 ChangelogViewer.xhtml now renders all entries again (was zero)',
'',
'### Security',
'- 🔒 No new SIN findings this cycle; 17 latent corruption markers eliminated',
'',
'### Pipeline Metrics',
'| 📊 Metric | Value |',
'|---|---|',
'| 🔁 Cycles run | 11 |',
'| 🎯 Targets | 5 |',
'| 📌 Open todos | 4 |',
'| ✅ Edited files clean | 6/6 |',
'',
'---',
'',
'## [2604.B2.V33.3] — 2026-04-16',
'',
'### Added',
'- 📄 `~README.md/CHANGELOG.md` — Standardised changelog (this file), retrofitted from ENHANCEMENTS-LOG.md',
'- 📄 `XHTML-ChangelogViewer.xhtml` — Interactive HTML changelog browser with filtering, date-range, search, diff comparison',
'- 📄 `scripts/Invoke-ChangelogDiff.ps1` — PowerShell script to generate `.mdv` virtual differential markdown files',
'- 📄 `styles/accent-changelog.css` — Accent CSS for changelog viewer (Teal `#2dd4bf`)',
'',
'### Changed',
'- 🔁 Pipeline cycle 10/10 — baseline health confirmed: 0 parse failures, 0 relics, 0 open todos',
'',
'### Fixed',
'- ⸸ No new SIN findings this cycle',
'',
'### Pipeline Metrics',
'| 📊 Metric | Value |',
'|---|---|',
'| 🐛 ParseFail | 0 ✅ |',
'| 🗑 Relics | 0 ✅ |',
'| 📌 OpenTodos | 0 ✅ |',
'| 📋 PlannedTodos | 69 |',
