'## [2604.B2.V33.1] — 2026-04-12',
'',
'### Added',
'- 📄 7× `.psd1` module manifests — `Get-LaunchTelemetry`, `PwShGUI-ConvoVault`, `PwShGUI-IntegrityCore`, `PwShGUI-NetworkTools`, `PwShGUI-SchemaTranslator`, `RE-memorAiZ`, `WorkspaceIntentReview`',
'',
