'',
'### Added',
'- 📄 `scripts/Invoke-StaticWorkspaceScan.ps1` — 6-phase static workspace scanner (folders→modules→scripts→configs→urls_ips→dns)',
'- 📄 `scripts/Invoke-EngineCrashCleanup.ps1` — Post-crash file quarantine and cleanup',
