'- 📄 `~README.md/CFRMENU-GUIDE.md` — 18-section CFRMenu user guide',
'- 📄 `~README.md/LAUNCH-GUI-ENHANCEMENT-PLAN.md` — 22-page master implementation plan',
'- 📄 `~README.md/LAUNCH-GUI-IMPLEMENTATION-CHECKLIST.md` — 120+ checkbox task breakdown',
