'',
'## [2603.B0.V27.4] — 2026-04-03',
'',
'### Added',
'- ⚙ `Invoke-WorkspaceDependencyMap.ps1` v2.0 — URL/IP extraction, DNS resolution, 3-tab XHTML output (graph, links, IP hit-rate), ZIP archive',
'- ⚙ `CronAiAthon-Scheduler.psm1` — Added `DepMap` task type',
'- ⚙ `cron-aiathon-schedule.json` — Added `TASK-DepMap` (daily, 1440min)',
'',
'### Changed',
'- ⚙ Dependency map exclusions: added `todo/`, `temp/`, swap extensions',
'',
'---',
'',
'## [2603.B0.V27.3] — 2026-03-28',
'',
'### Added',
'- 📄 `modules/CronAiAthon-Pipeline.psm1` — 12-function pipeline registry (CRUD, analytics, sin feedback, master aggregation)',
'- 📄 `modules/CronAiAthon-BugTracker.psm1` — 6-vector automated bug detection (parse, XHTML, crash logs, error traps, JSON, dependencies)',
'- 📄 `modules/CronAiAthon-Scheduler.psm1` — 15-function task scheduling engine (5 default cron jobs)',
'- 📄 `modules/CronAiAthon-EventLog.psm1` — Windows Event Log + SYSLOG (RFC 5424 UDP/TCP)',
