'### 🖥 `scripts/Start-LocalWebEngine.ps1` — Bootstrap Logging & Crash Detection',
'⚙ New `$script:BootstrapLogFile = logs\\engine-bootstrap.log` written before HttpListener starts  ',
'⚙ New `$script:CrashLogFile = logs\\engine-crash.log`; `$script:_ExitClean = $false` dirty-exit flag  ',
'📝 New `Write-BootstrapLog` function: logs port pre-check, config load, module import, listener bind  ',
