'⸸ P009 guarded — `$WorkspacePath` validated before `Join-Path` calls  ',
'⸸ P012 guarded — `Set-Content -Encoding UTF8` on all log writes  ',
'⚙ New routes: `GET /api/engine/events` (aggregate all logs, `?tail=N`), `GET /api/engine/logs/list`  ',
'⚙ `Handle-EngineEvents` parses `[ts][LEVEL] msg` and `[ts][BOOT][LEVEL] msg` formats; returns `{source, ts, level, msg}[]`  ',
