'### 📄 New: `scripts/Invoke-StaticWorkspaceScan.ps1` (v32.0)',
'⚙ 6 independent scan phases via `try{} catch{ continue }` — no phase blocks another  ',
'📌 **Phase inventory:** `folders` → `modules` → `scripts` → `configs` → `urls_ips` → `dns_resolution`  ',
'📝 Writes `logs/scan-progress.json` (mode:`Static`) after every phase  ',
