'⸸ P005 guarded — PS 5.1 only, no `??`/`?.`  ',
'⸸ P009 guarded — `$WorkspacePath` validated at entry  ',
'⸸ P021 guarded — zero-division on `durationMs` checked  ',
'⸸ P027 guarded — FIX-B `.Count` preconditions before array index  ',
'💡 Use `-Phases \'folders,modules\'` to run a subset; `-SkipDns` to skip DNS resolution  ',
'',
'### 📄 New: `scripts/Invoke-EngineCrashCleanup.ps1` (v32.0)',
