'- **Troubleshooting Guide:** Common issues, causes, solutions',
'',
'### 📐 SIN Compliance',
'All new PowerShell scripts validated against:',
'- ⸸ **P004:** All `.Count` operations wrapped with `@()` force-array',
'- ⸸ **P005:** No PS7-only operators (`??`, `?.`, `??=`)',
'- ⸸ **P012/P017/P019:** All file operations specify `-Encoding UTF8` explicitly',
'- ⸸ **P014:** `ConvertTo-Json` uses `-Depth 5` (default 2 truncates nested objects)',
'- ⸸ **P015:** No hardcoded absolute paths (use `$PSScriptRoot`, `Join-Path`)',
'- ⸸ **P022:** Null guards before method calls (`if ($null -ne $obj)` before `$obj.Method()`)',
'- ⚑ **SS-005:** All exported functions include `[CmdletBinding()]` attribute',
'',
'### Backup & Safety',
'- Created `Launch-GUI.bat.backup_2604` before modifications',
'- All new files follow VersionTag standard: `2604.B1.v1.0` (YYMM.B#.v<major>.<minor>)',
'- All scripts include header: Author, Date, VersionTag, FileRole, Purpose',
'',
