'## ⚙ 2026-06-05 — Session 9: Checklists Tab, Security Tests, CertMonitor, PKI Tests',
'',
'### Show-CronAiAthonTool.ps1 — Checklists Tab (new Tab 7)',
'- Added nested TabControl with 5 sub-tabs: **View** (filterable read-only browse of all todo/ items via Get-CentralMasterToDo), **Add & Modify** (create/edit JSON todo items with save-to-disk), **Review & Approve** (approve/reject items in REVIEW/OPEN/PLANNED status, writes status change to JSON files), **Event Log** (reads action-log.json + CronAiAthon event log JSONs filtered to checklist/todo operations), **Pipeline Summary** (status breakdown grid + health metrics RTF panel from Get-PipelineHealthMetrics)',
'- Inner sub-tabs auto-load on tab selection via $innerTabs.Add_SelectedIndexChanged and $tabCtrl.Add_SelectedIndexChanged hooks',
'',
'### Show-CronAiAthonTool.ps1 — Master ToDo Tab revamped (Tab 8, was Tab 7)',
'- **Removed:** "Aggregate & Load" admin button',
'- **Added:** Telemetry banner strip (Total/Open/In Prog/Done/HIGH Pri/Bugs/Features/ToDos counts)',
'- **Added:** Filter bar: Type, Status, Priority, Source, free-text search — all applied via Apply-MasterFilter without reloading from disk',
'- **Auto-load:** Invoke-MasterRefresh called via $tabCtrl.Add_SelectedIndexChanged whenever Master ToDo tab is selected',
'- Grid remains fully read-only (no edit tools)',
'',
'### tests/Invoke-SecurityIntegrityTests.ps1 (new)',
'- 10-test security scan suite covering: hardcoded credentials (P001/OWASP A02), Invoke-Expression injection (P010/OWASP A03), path traversal (P009), plaintext private key writes, sensitive keyword exposure in logs, vault access pattern integrity, critical module SHA256 hash baseline verification, privilege escalation indicators, empty catch blocks (P002), UTF-8 BOM check (P006)',
'- Outputs structured JSON report to 	emp/security-integrity-report.json; -FailOnCritical exits with code 1',
'',
'### tests/PKIChainManager.Tests.ps1 (fleshed out, was stub)',
'- Expanded from 3 stub tests to 40+ assertions across 7 Describe blocks: Module Surface, Initialize-PKIChainManager, Pre-initialisation guard, New-RootCACertificate, New-SubordinateCACertificate, New-CodeSignCertificate, Get-PKIChainStatus, Export-CertToVault, New-FullPKIChain',
'- Tests use TestDrive temp paths; certs cleaned from store in AfterAll blocks',
'- Validates EXPIRING threshold (90 days), Code Signing EKU OID (1.3.6.1.5.5.7.3.3), vault mock isolation',
'',
'### config/cron-aiathon-schedule.json — CertMonitor task added',
'- New task: TASK-CertMonitor — type CertMonitor, frequency 1440 min (daily), enabled by default',
'- Scans pki/ folder tree for .cer files, computes days-until-expiry per cert, writes JSON report to ~REPORTS/CertMonitor/',
'- Handler in CronAiAthon-Scheduler.psm1: calls Write-CronLog -Severity Warning for EXPIRED/EXPIRING certs',
'',
'### modules/CronAiAthon-Scheduler.psm1 — CertMonitor switch case',
'- Added CertMonitor case in Invoke-CronJob switch (after DepMap); scans PKI path, writes per-run JSON report, logs expired/expiring certs',
'',
