'## ⚙ 2026-04-03 — Session 8: Dependency Map v2.0 — URL/IP Scanner, DNS Resolution, XHTML Visualisation, ZIP Archive',
'',
'### Invoke-WorkspaceDependencyMap.ps1 v2.0 (extended)',
'- **Exclusions:** Added `todo/` and `temp/` folders to `$script:ExcludeNames`; added temp/swap extension filter (`.tmp .bak .log .lock .pyc .pyo .cache` and `~`-prefix filenames) to `$allFiles` collection',
'- **URL/IP Extraction (Phase 3 + 4):** Added `$urlRegex` and `$ipv4Regex` patterns; every scanned code and config file now has `urls`/`ips` arrays extracted and stored on node objects and in `$urlIpMap` hashtable',
'- **DNS Resolution (Phase 4b — new):** Resolves all unique hostnames from extracted URLs via `[System.Net.Dns]::GetHostAddresses()`; stores per-host `{ ips, error, hits }` in `$dnsResolution`; skippable with `-SkipDns`',
'- **IP Hit-Rate Table:** Builds `$ipHitRate` mapping each IPv4 (direct refs + DNS-resolved) to all files referencing it; sorted descending by file count as `$ipHitRateList`',
'- **ZIP Archive:** Compresses output JSON using `System.IO.Compression.ZipFile` to `workspace-dependency-map-{ts}.zip`; skippable with `-SkipZip`',
'- **XHTML Output (full replacement):** Replaced single-tab dark HTML graph with 3-tab XHTML 1.1 document:',
'  - **Tab 1 — Graph:** SVG force-directed dependency graph (folder/module/script/config nodes, pan/zoom/filter/relax)',
'  - **Tab 2 — Links & IPs:** Filterable/sortable table of every file\'s URLs (clickable `<a href>`) and direct IPv4 refs',
'  - **Tab 3 — IP Hit Rate:** Filterable/sortable IP frequency table with DNS-resolved hostname column and per-file file list',
'- **New JSON fields:** `urlIpByFile`, `dnsResolution`, `ipHitRate`, `summary.urlFileCount`, `summary.uniqueHosts`, `summary.uniqueIPs`',
'- **New params:** `-SkipHtml`, `-SkipZip`, `-SkipDns`',
'',
'### CronAiAthon-Scheduler.psm1 (extended)',
'- **Added `\'DepMap\'` task type** to `Invoke-CronJob` switch block — runs `Invoke-WorkspaceDependencyMap.ps1` on schedule',
'',
'### cron-aiathon-schedule.json (extended)',
'- **Added `TASK-DepMap`** — daily (1440 min frequency), type `DepMap`, initially enabled; regenerates dep-map JSON/XHTML/ZIP once per day',
'',
'### FILES-MANIFEST.md (updated)',
'- Added `Invoke-WorkspaceDependencyMap.ps1` entries to both the summary section and the detailed section',
'',
