'- **Created `modules/CronAiAthon-BugTracker.psm1`** — 6-vector automated bug detection (8 functions)',
'  - `Invoke-ParseCheck` — PowerShell AST parse error scanner across workspace .ps1/.psm1 files',
'  - `Invoke-XhtmlValidation` — XHTML well-formedness and tag-balance checking',
'  - `Invoke-CrashLogScan` — Scans logs/ for crash/exception/fatal patterns',
'  - `Invoke-ErrorTrapAudit` — Finds unprotected file/network/JSON operations without try/catch',
