'  - `Register-SubagentCall` / `Register-Question` — Cross-agent call tally and question registry',
'',
'### CronAiAthon-EventLog Module (new)',
'- **Created `modules/CronAiAthon-EventLog.psm1`** — Windows Event Log + SYSLOG (8 functions)',
'  - `Register-EventLogSources` — PowerShellGUI-CRON, PowerShellGUI-CORE in Application log',
'  - `Write-CronEventLog` — Tagged with SYSLOG severity (Emergency=0 through Debug=7)',
'  - `Send-SyslogMessage` — RFC 5424 UDP 161 primary, TCP 161 fallback',
'  - `Write-SyslogFile` — Local `logs/PowerShellGUI.SYSLOG` file',
'  - `Write-CronLog` — Unified: EventLog + .SYSLOG + optional network forwarding',
'  - SYSLOG severity-to-EventLog mapping: 0-3=Error, 4=Warning, 5-7=Information',
'',
