'## 🚀 Usage',
'',
'### Run the Application',
'```bash',
'# Option 1: Double-click',
'Launch-GUI.bat',
'',
'# Option 2: PowerShell',
'powershell.exe -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File Main-GUI.ps1',
'```',
'',
'### View Logs',
'```bash',
'# Open logs directory',
'Get-ChildItem C:\\PowerShellGUI\\logs\\',
'',
'# View today\'s log',
'Get-Content "C:\\PowerShellGUI\\logs\\COMPUTERNAME-$(Get-Date -Format \'yyyy-MM-dd\').log"',
'',
'# View specific event types',
'Get-Content "C:\\PowerShellGUI\\logs\\*.log" | Where-Object { $_ -match \'\\[Event\\]\' }',
'```',
'',
'### Filter Logs by Level',
'```powershell',
'# Show only events',
'Get-Content "C:\\PowerShellGUI\\logs\\*.log" | Where-Object { $_ -match \'\\[Event\\]\' }',
'',
'# Show only errors',
'Get-Content "C:\\PowerShellGUI\\logs\\*.log" | Where-Object { $_ -match \'\\[Error\\]\' }',
'',
'# Show only debug info',
'Get-Content "C:\\PowerShellGUI\\logs\\*.log" | Where-Object { $_ -match \'\\[Debug\\]\' }',
'```',
'',
