'',
'### 🛡️ Safety Scoring System',
'',
'**Function:** `Get-ScriptSafetyScore`',
'',
'**Scoring Logic:**',
'- Starts at 100 (perfectly safe)',
'- Deducts penalty for each risky pattern found',
'- Min score: 0, Max score: 100',
'',
'**Penalty Values:**',
'',
'| Pattern | Penalty |',
'|---------|--------|',
'| Invoke-Expression | 12 |',
'| Download and Execute | 18 |',
'| Execution Policy Change | 8 |',
'| Recursive Force Delete | 10 |',
'| RunAs Elevation | 8 |',
'| Scheduled Task | 10 |',
'| Security Settings | 8 |',
'| Service Control | 8 |',
'| System Power | 10 |',
'| Registry Edit | 10 |',
'| Password/API Key/Secret | 20 each |',
'',
'**Integration:**',
'- Logged before script execution',
'- Used to determine `-WhatIf` usage',
'- Displayed in safety badge',
'',
'**Code Location:** Lines 1074-1131',
'',
'---',
'',
'### 🏷️ Safety Badge in Elevation Prompt',
'',
'**What It Shows:**',
'- Script safety score (0-100)',
'- Color coding:',
'  - 🟢 Green: 80-100 (Safe)',
'  - 🟡 Yellow: 50-79 (Moderate)',
'  - 🔴 Red: 0-49 (Risky)',
'- Auto `-WhatIf` indicator',
'- Key findings summary',
'',
'**Example Prompt:**',
'```',
'╔══════════════════════════════════════╗',
'║  Admin Elevation Request             ║',
'╠══════════════════════════════════════╣',
'║  Script: Script4.ps1                 ║',
'║  Safety Score: 82/100 🟢              ║',
'║  Status: Safe to run                 ║',
'╚══════════════════════════════════════╝',
'',
'Run with administrator privileges?',
'```',
'',
'**Code Location:** Lines 850-890 (to be updated)',
'',
'---',
'',
'### ⚠️ Auto WhatIf for Moderate Scripts',
'',
'**Logic:**',
'- Scripts with safety score > 50 automatically get `-WhatIf`',
'- Only if script supports `-WhatIf` parameter',
'- Logged before execution',
'- Applied to both admin and non-admin runs',
'',
'**Code Integration:**',
'```powershell',
'$supportsWhatIf = $cmd.Parameters.ContainsKey(\'WhatIf\')',
'$useWhatIf = ($safetyScore -gt 50 -and $supportsWhatIf)',
'',
'if ($useWhatIf) {',
'    & $scriptPath -WhatIf',
'} else {',
'    & $scriptPath',
'}',
'```',
'',
'**Code Location:** Lines 823-855',
'',
'---',
