'## 2026-03-28 — Session 7: Cron-Ai-Athon Pipeline, Scheduler, Bug Tracker, EventLog/SYSLOG',
'',
'### CronAiAthon-Pipeline Module (new)',
'- **Created `modules/CronAiAthon-Pipeline.psm1`** — Unified pipeline registry (12 exported functions)',
'  - `New-PipelineItem` — Schema: id, type, title, description, priority, status, source, category, sessionModCount',
'  - `Initialize-PipelineRegistry` — Creates `config/cron-aiathon-pipeline.json` with schema metadata',
'  - `Add-PipelineItem` / `Update-PipelineItemStatus` — CRUD with auto-increment sessionModCount',
'  - `Get-PipelineItems` / `Get-PipelineStatistics` — Query and analytics',
'  - `Invoke-SinRegistryFeedback` — Compares bugs against sin_registry JSON, creates sins for new patterns',
'  - `ConvertTo-Bugs2FIX` / `ConvertTo-Items2ADD` — Type promotion helpers',
'  - `Get-CentralMasterToDo` — Aggregates from pipeline, todo/ folder, FeatureRequests JSON, BugTracker JSON',
'  - `Export-CentralMasterToDo` — Writes `todo/_master-aggregated.json` with typed/status breakdowns',
'',
'### CronAiAthon-BugTracker Module (new)',
'- **Created `modules/CronAiAthon-BugTracker.psm1`** — 6-vector automated bug detection (8 functions)',
'  - `Invoke-ParseCheck` — PowerShell AST parse error scanner across workspace .ps1/.psm1 files',
'  - `Invoke-XhtmlValidation` — XHTML well-formedness and tag-balance checking',
'  - `Invoke-CrashLogScan` — Scans logs/ for crash/exception/fatal patterns',
'  - `Invoke-ErrorTrapAudit` — Finds unprotected file/network/JSON operations without try/catch',
'  - `Invoke-DataValidationCheck` — Tests JSON file parse validity across config/ and scripts/',
'  - `Invoke-DependencyCheck` — Validates module/script file existence and Requires tags',
'  - `Invoke-FullBugScan` — Runs all 6 vectors, returns consolidated results',
'  - `Invoke-BugToPipelineProcessor` — Auto-pushes detected bugs into CronAiAthon-Pipeline',
'',
'### CronAiAthon-Scheduler Module (new)',
'- **Created `modules/CronAiAthon-Scheduler.psm1`** — Task scheduling engine (15 functions)',
'  - 5 default cron jobs: BugScan (120min), PipelineProcess (60min), MasterAggregate (30min), SinRegistryReview (240min), PreReqCheck (480min)',
'  - Job statistics: cycles, errors, itemsDone, bugsFound, testsMade, plansMade, subagentCalls, questions',
'  - `Invoke-PreRequisiteCheck` — Validates 7 directories, 4 modules, pipeline config, schedule config',
'  - `Invoke-CronJob` / `Invoke-AllCronJobs` — Execute tasks by type or run full cycle',
'  - `Add-AutopilotSuggestion` / `Update-AutopilotSuggestionStatus` — Self-improvement tracking',
'  - `Register-SubagentCall` / `Register-Question` — Cross-agent call tally and question registry',
'',
'### CronAiAthon-EventLog Module (new)',
'- **Created `modules/CronAiAthon-EventLog.psm1`** — Windows Event Log + SYSLOG (8 functions)',
'  - `Register-EventLogSources` — PowerShellGUI-CRON, PowerShellGUI-CORE in Application log',
'  - `Write-CronEventLog` — Tagged with SYSLOG severity (Emergency=0 through Debug=7)',
'  - `Send-SyslogMessage` — RFC 5424 UDP 161 primary, TCP 161 fallback',
'  - `Write-SyslogFile` — Local `logs/PowerShellGUI.SYSLOG` file',
'  - `Write-CronLog` — Unified: EventLog + .SYSLOG + optional network forwarding',
'  - SYSLOG severity-to-EventLog mapping: 0-3=Error, 4=Warning, 5-7=Information',
'',
'### Show-CronAiAthonTool GUI (new)',
'- **Created `scripts/Show-CronAiAthonTool.ps1`** — 12-tab WinForms dashboard',
'  - Tab 1: Dashboard overview (metrics, queue, statistics, questions summary)',
'  - Tab 2: Task Schedule (DataGridView, global frequency, load/apply)',
'  - Tab 3: Pre-Req Checks (pass/fail/warn colored results)',
'  - Tab 4: Manual Runner (select task, run selected/all, RichTextBox results)',
'  - Tab 5: Pipeline Queue (filter by type/status, DataGridView)',
'  - Tab 6: Bug Tracker (full scan, push to pipeline)',
