'## 🔧 Issues Fixed',
'',
'### Issue 1: No GUI Displayed on Startup',
'**Problem:** GUI window wasn\\'t appearing when application started  ',
'**Root Cause:** `[void]$form.ShowDialog()` was suppressing the dialog output  ',
'**Solution:** Changed to `$form.ShowDialog() | Out-Null` to properly display the form',
'',
'### Issue 2: Insufficient Event Logging',
'**Problem:** Lack of detailed event tracking for user interactions  ',
'**Solution:** Added comprehensive event logging throughout the application',
'',
'---',
'',
'## ✨ Enhancements Made',
'',
'### New Log Levels',
'Added two new logging levels for better visibility:',
'',
'| Level | Color | Purpose |',
'|-------|-------|---------|',
'| **Event** | Cyan | User interactions and important events |',
'| **Debug** | Gray | Detailed diagnostic information |',
'',
'### Events Now Logged',
'',
'#### GUI Interactions',
'- Button clicks with script name and display name',
'- Menu selections (File, Tests, Links, WinGets, Tools, Help)',
'- About dialog access',
'',
'#### Admin Elevation',
'- Admin elevation prompt display',
'- User response (YES/NO)',
'- Elevation request details',
'',
'#### Configuration & Logs',
'- Config file initialization',
'- Config file viewing attempts',
'- Logs directory access',
'',
'#### Application Lifecycle',
'- Application startup with system info',
'- GUI form display',
'- GUI form closure',
'- Application shutdown',
'',
'#### Script Execution',
'- Script launch requests',
'- Script name and display name',
'- Admin elevation status',
'- Execution completion',
'',
'---',
'',
