'',
'**Before:**',
'```powershell',
'[ValidateSet("Info", "Warning", "Error", "Success")]',
'```',
'',
'**After:**',
'```powershell',
'[ValidateSet("Info", "Warning", "Error", "Success", "Debug", "Event")]',
'```',
'',
