'$form.ShowDialog() | Out-Null',
'Write-Log "GUI form closed by user" "Event"',
'```',
'',
'---',
'',
'### 9. Main Execution Block',
'**Location:** Lines 347-365  ',
'**Changes:**',
'- Added separator lines for log readability',
'- Enhanced startup logging',
'- Added try-catch error handling',
'- More detailed system information in logs',
'',
'**Added Logging:**',
'```powershell',
'Write-Log "=====================================================================" "Event"',
'Write-Log "PowerShell GUI Application starting..." "Info"',
'Write-Log "Computer: $env:COMPUTERNAME | User: $env:USERNAME | PowerShell: $($PSVersionTable.PSVersion)" "Info"',
'try {',
'    Create-GUI',
'}',
'catch {',
'    Write-Log "Error in GUI creation: $_" "Error"',
'}',
'```',
'',
