'### 🔄 Conditional Version Auto-Increment',
'',
'**What Changed:**',
'- Version check now runs FIRST before any auto-increment',
'- User prompted only when mismatches detected',
'- Color-coded console output (Blue=match, Red=mismatch)',
'- User types "AA" to authorize increment',
'- No timeout - user control over increment decision',
'',
'**Flow:**',
'1. **Phase 1:** `Test-VersionTag` scans all files',
'2. **Phase 2:** Parse XML diff for mismatches',
'3. **Phase 3:** Display results:',
'   - **All Match:** Blue message, skip increment',
'   - **Mismatches:** Red message, list issues, prompt for "AA"',
'4. **Phase 4:** Generate manifest',
'5. **Phase 5:** Display system info',
'',
'**Code Location:** Lines 1599-1673',
